Valero Flares During Maintenance at Houston Oil Refinery

-- B y   L e e l a   L a n d r e s s
-- 
2011-02-24T18:52:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/valero-starts-maintenance-expects-flaring-at-houston-refinery.html
  Valero Energy Corp . expected to
flare during planned maintenance at its Houston refinery,
according to a message left on a community hot line.  The message left today was related to the restart of a
crude unit at the refinery, Bill Day, a San Antonio-based
company spokesman said today in an e-mail.  The refinery, which is located on the  Houston Ship Channel ,
has a capacity of 145,000 barrels a day, according to data
compiled by Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Leela Landress in Houston at 
 llandress@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Marino at 
 dmarino4@bloomberg.net  